subject: 2 More Videos up on YouTube
author: Steve Hultay
full_text:
I did 2 more videos, one with the 20-125 and the other with the 12-
820.  After the session with the 20-125 i realized that i do not get 
along with the spirits on the FM band.  I know it sounds silly, but

that to me, is there different spirits on different bands ???

-Steve H.
